<h1><u><b>Meet the Tekton Management Team</b></u></h1>

<div style="text-align: center;">
  <img src="https://assets.onecompiler.app/43msdrzmd/43msdhkhy/IMG_7373.jpg" alt="Photo of CEO" width="250"><br>
  <span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px;">Founder</span><br>
  <span style="font-size: 16px; font-style: italic;">Tayseer Wahbeh</span>
</div>
<p class="bio"><b>Tekton</b> is led by a diverse and talented executive team focused on innovation and excellence in the construction industry. From strategy to operations, our leadership is <i>committed</i> to delivering high-quality solutions for modern building challenges.</p>

<h2>Our Executive Leaders</h2>
<ul>
  <li><b>Luke Geiger</b> – <span class="highlight">Chief Executive Officer</span><br>Luke has 25 years of experience in structural engineering and oversees all strategic direction.</li>
  <li><b>Charlie Kauffman</b> – <span class="highlight">Chief Operating Officer</span><br>Charlie ensures efficient daily operations, manages logistics, and leads the workforce development program.</li>
  <li><b>Kai Lannon</b> – <span class="highlight">Chief Financial Officer</span><br>Kai brings deep financial acumen to manage capital, investments, and risk strategy.</li>
  <li><b>Andrew Sobczak</b> – <span class="highlight">Chief Technology Officer</span><br>Andrew leads R&D and is the brain behind our SmartBuild AI platform.</li>
</ul>

<h2>Major Team Milestones</h2>
<ol>
  <li>Expanded operations to three new international markets in under two years.</li>
  <li>Achieved 40% year-over-year growth in project volume.</li>
  <li>Implemented Tekton’s cloud-based tracking system company-wide.</li>
</ol>

<p>For insights into strong leadership in construction, check out this <a href="https://www.criterionhcm.com/blog/leadership-styles-in-the-construction-industry" target="_blank">article on construction leadership</a>.</p>

